"""
genie_bot_streamlit_poc.py  —  Genie Bot L1/L2 Support PoC
===========================================================

Flow:
  1. User pastes log → clicks Diagnose
  2. RAG API called → L1 resolution shown
  3. User tries fix manually
  4. If still broken → clicks "Escalate to L2"
  5. RAG API called again → pre-filled L2 template shown as-is

RAG spec:
  POST /generation/{usecase_id}/{pipeline_id}
  Header : AMToken = <JWT>
  Body   : { "query": "...", "history": [{"question":"...","answer":"..."}] }

JWT: OpenAM → SSO tokenId → JWT (expires 30s, auto-refreshes every 25s)
"""

